Create a key pair with (RSA and 2,048-bit keys):
gpg --gen-key
Now export yourpublic key using the form of:
gpg --export -a "Your name" > mypub.key
Now export yourprivate key using the form of:gpg --export-secret-key -a "Your name" > mypriv.key

How is the randomness generated?
